I get it. I do.

33:41.333 --> 33:44.667
- But we're friends, right?
- Yeah.

33:59.208 --> 34:01.333
Hey, Brian.

34:01.333 --> 34:03.667
Just so you know, despite...

34:04.250 --> 34:06.083
...everything...

34:06.750 --> 34:08.834
I'm not trouble.

34:08.834 --> 34:10.250
That's what you think.

34:13.041 --> 34:15.166
OK, maybe a little bit.

34:24.667 --> 34:27.208
[Dave] Just don't think
that the Berlin Wall is

34:27.208 --> 34:29.667
the most important event
of the 20th century.

34:29.667 --> 34:33.041
It was a major shift in people's
perceptions of the world.

34:33.041 --> 34:36.166
Really? More than a man
walking on the moon?

34:36.166 --> 34:37.875
What?! That doesn't affect us.

34:37.875 --> 34:41.875
That wall coming down was
so much bigger than just a wall.

34:41.875 --> 34:43.458
You know what I mean?

34:46.583 --> 34:49.792
- God, I don't wanna
say good night.
- I don't either.

34:49.792 --> 34:53.458
[soft music plays]

34:53.458 --> 34:55.375
♪ Dream ♪

34:55.375 --> 34:58.709
♪ I wanna feel you breathe ♪

34:58.709 --> 35:02.166
♪ Baby, don't you wake up ♪

35:02.166 --> 35:05.083
♪ I wanna watch you sleep ♪

35:05.083 --> 35:07.542
OK, I gotta tell you something.

35:07.542 --> 35:10.625
I don't want to lie to you.
I just wanna tell you the truth.

35:10.625 --> 35:12.583
You're gay. I knew it.

35:12.583 --> 35:15.291
No, I'm not gay.
What do you mean, you knew it?

35:15.291 --> 35:19.709
Good job. You're smart, single.
What else could explain it?

35:19.709 --> 35:24.583
I'm getting divorced
and, uh, I have three kids.

35:24.583 --> 35:27.166
Oh, that's cool.

35:31.125 --> 35:33.291
I have something
I have to tell you, too.

35:33.291 --> 35:34.917
OK.

35:34.917 --> 35:38.625
I live with my parents
and I'm only 21.

35:38.625 --> 35:41.417
Well, almost. Next month.

35:45.333 --> 35:47.333
Wow.

35:53.875 --> 35:55.959
- Whoa, you leaving so soon?
- Well...

35:55.959 --> 35:58.792
- We thought...
- Kidding. You got
something to sign?

35:58.792 --> 36:00.458
Uh...

36:00.458 --> 36:02.458
You know, you guys
worked pretty hard.

36:02.458 --> 36:04.875
That is not unimpressive.

36:04.875 --> 36:06.834
Yeah, well,
you guys do good work.

36:06.834 --> 36:10.041
Every little bit helps,
you know what I'm saying?

36:10.041 --> 36:13.166
- Every little bit.
- [man] See you later.

36:13.166 --> 36:15.250
[man 2] Take it easy, bro.

36:15.250 --> 36:20.583
Hey, Adam, next time
you sneak out, bring me
back some damn fries.

36:27.625 --> 36:30.291
How'd it go last night?

36:30.291 --> 36:32.417
You ever wonder
why we do this?

36:37.750 --> 36:42.583
I mean, why we always
help the wrong people?

36:42.583 --> 36:45.667
You really think these guys
are only looking for 750,000?

36:47.417 --> 36:49.041
You never know.

36:52.208 --> 36:55.709
Turkey, PB and J. Ham and
strawberry. Those are good.

36:55.709 --> 36:59.458
This is good. More strawberry.
Here, more strawberry
and cheese.

36:59.458 --> 37:02.542
That'll work. Cheese.

37:02.542 --> 37:04.875
Honey, honey, honey,
what are you doing?

37:04.875 --> 37:07.959
Daddy, please,
no more sandwiches.

37:07.959 --> 37:10.417
We had them yesterday.
And for dinner.

37:10.417 --> 37:12.542
- I like them.
- OK, you know what? Fine.

37:12.542 --> 37:15.542
No more sandwiches.
You'll have apples, a little
cheese.

37:15.542 --> 37:18.250
- [girls] Mommy!
- Hey! Hi!

37:18.250 --> 37:22.667
Oh, I know.
I missed you. I missed you.

37:22.667 --> 37:26.542
And I missed you.
I missed you. I did.

37:26.542 --> 37:29.166
OK, you ready to go?
Let's do it, monkey lovers.

37:29.166 --> 37:32.291
Get shoes on. You're gonna
be late for school. Come on.

37:34.458 --> 37:37.583
So I thought you were
gonna be at Nic's until dinner.

37:37.583 --> 37:42.709
Oh, no. I just...
I just wanted to be home.

37:42.709 --> 37:46.417
- So how did your date go?
- Good. Fine. Yours?

37:46.417 --> 37:50.083
Awesome.
What'd you guys do?

37:50.083 --> 37:55.750
Just dinner. You know,
it was fine, really.
Nothing special.

37:55.750 --> 38:00.834
Well, I just wanted to
thank you for the advice.
You know, I kept it simple.

38:00.834 --> 38:03.291
It was fun.
We went to an arcade.

38:04.375 --> 38:05.709
That sounds like fun.

38:05.709 --> 38:08.291
Yeah, it was. We played
video games all night.

38:08.291 --> 38:11.417
- Ate funnel cake.
- Sounds like the
perfect date for you.

38:11.417 --> 38:13.750
Know what? It kinda was.
It was a good time.

38:13.750 --> 38:17.125
I don't know, there...
There was this connection
between us.

38:17.125 --> 38:19.417
- OK, you know what?
Dave, I get it.
- What?

38:19.417 --> 38:23.458
Look, Dave, I know
what we talked about,

38:23.458 --> 38:25.625
and I know that
when some people break up,

38:25.625 --> 38:28.166
they try really hard
to be friends,

38:28.166 --> 38:31.458
you know, to be together,
like nothing's changed.

38:31.458 --> 38:35.500
But things have changed.
And, uh...

38:35.500 --> 38:38.458
I don't wanna give you
advice about dating. You know?

38:38.458 --> 38:40.959
- It's hard for me.
- OK.

38:40.959 --> 38:43.875
So I think that, maybe,
just for now, I think...

38:45.250 --> 38:47.250
I think we shouldn't
talk for a while.

38:48.417 --> 38:50.458
Not talk? It's a little...

38:50.458 --> 38:52.625
I mean, we gotta
talk about the kids.

38:52.625 --> 38:55.166
Yes, of course, we
will, obviously.

38:55.166 --> 38:59.000
But I just don't think
we should do this kind of thing.

38:59.000 --> 39:00.083
I just... I can't.

39:00.083 --> 39:03.166
Here you go.
Is that what you want?

39:03.166 --> 39:05.166
OK?

39:05.166 --> 39:07.125
Hi.

39:07.125 --> 39:12.250
I tried everything.
[sighs] Two hours
on a swing set, hiking,

39:12.250 --> 39:16.000
castor oil,
this awful salad dressing.

39:16.000 --> 39:18.166
- At the restaurant
at the ocean?
- Yeah!

39:18.166 --> 39:20.709
I can still feel it on my teeth.
It was horrible.

39:20.709 --> 39:24.542
If you don't go into labor
by next week, I'll induce.

39:24.542 --> 39:29.333
Next week? Oh, no. I don't...
I don't think I can take it.

39:29.333 --> 39:32.166
- Why won't she come out?
- You better get used to it.

39:32.166 --> 39:35.333
You'll be fighting
plenty as soon as
she's out of the womb.

39:35.333 --> 39:38.625
I have two girls.
A three-year old and a teenager.

39:38.625 --> 39:42.291
It doesn't change,
unfortunately.
Neither one listens to me.

39:42.291 --> 39:47.083
- My mother says it's karma.
- Karma?

39:47.083 --> 39:49.834
I hope you were nicer to
your mom than I was to mine.

39:50.458 --> 39:52.291
[sighs]

39:52.291 --> 39:56.750
[♪ Frou Frou: Only Got One]

39:56.750 --> 40:00.709
You were right. This guy's
a shark. Someone's gunning
for partner.

40:00.709 --> 40:02.375
I talked to opposing counsel.

40:02.375 --> 40:04.667
This guy saved us
half a million dollars.

40:04.667 --> 40:09.750
- Miller settled
for two-point-five.
- Two-point-five?

40:09.750 --> 40:12.750
Oh, what can I say?
I'm a shark.

40:12.750 --> 40:16.417
Nice work, Hillman. Very nice.

40:16.417 --> 40:19.333
- Yeah, nice work.
- What?

40:19.333 --> 40:21.542
Maybe the lawyer had
a change of heart.

40:21.542 --> 40:23.917
Yeah. I guess he did.

40:24.709 --> 40:26.041
[scoffs]

40:29.125 --> 40:33.667
♪ If I chose to spite you ♪

40:34.917 --> 40:36.083
Brian...

40:38.500 --> 40:42.417
♪ Will song turn to silence? ♪

40:42.417 --> 40:44.458
I didn't want you
to have to go it alone.

40:47.917 --> 40:52.417
♪ Are you down
just to be down? ♪

40:52.417 --> 40:57.792
♪ I don't believe the words
you sing sometimes ♪

40:57.792 --> 41:02.125
♪ But, then, it's your life ♪

41:02.125 --> 41:07.458
♪ Mm-hmm, it's your life ♪

41:07.458 --> 41:11.458
♪ It's your life ♪

41:11.458 --> 41:14.500
♪ But, you've only got one ♪

41:14.500 --> 41:16.125
Hi, honey.

41:17.792 --> 41:21.000
- ♪ Life ♪
- ♪ But, you've only got one ♪

41:21.000 --> 41:22.667
Hi, Mom.

41:22.667 --> 41:27.750
- ♪ Life ♪
- ♪ But, you've only got one ♪

41:27.750 --> 41:32.583
Well, what do you know?

41:32.583 --> 41:36.709
- ♪ Life ♪
- ♪ But, you've only got one ♪

41:36.709 --> 41:41.083
- ♪ Life ♪
- ♪ But, you've only got one ♪

41:43.291 --> 41:45.917
[both laughing]

41:49.291 --> 41:50.834
My little girl.

41:57.834 --> 42:02.000
[exhales] Come in. Come in.

42:06.417 --> 42:11.125
♪ But you've only got one ♪♪

